_sText:
Hello again. This is V2 of my deathrun map. I deleted the Penis Trap and made a new Penis Trap which is much easier. The box with 1-2-3-4-5-6 is now made easier. One trap was removed full and i made a new one out of it.
One of the traps is from an other map but only because one of the members asked for it.
I'm sorry for that.
I build all on my own.
I didn't steal any work from other maps.

So have fun with my map.
